Second Department,

Mat, 1953.

(May 4, 1953.) Algonquin Gas Transmission Company, Appellant, v. E. W. Realty Corporation, Respondent, et al., Defendants. (Proceeding No. 1.) (And Ten Other Proceedings.)

— Motion to recall remittitur and, upon such recall, to resettle orders denied, without costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Carswell, Adel and Wenzel, JJ.; Beldock, J., not voting. [See ante, pp. 898, 983.]
